
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Standard Demo | Love Crafted Digital</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1e293b, #020617 60%);
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }
    .wrap {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2.8rem 1.3rem 3.5rem;
    }
    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }
    .logo-img {
      height: 46px;
      width: auto;
      display: block;
    }
    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: .8rem;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-left: 1.4rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .16em;
    }
    nav a:hover {
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }
    .hero {
      display: grid;
      gap: 2.2rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      .hero {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
        align-items: center;
      }
    }
    h1 {
      font-family: "DM Serif Display", serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      margin-bottom: .9rem;
    }
    h1 span {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #fbbf24, #60a5fa);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
    }
    .lede {
      color: #9ca3af;
      max-width: 30rem;
      font-size: .96rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: .75rem 1.6rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #60a5fa;
      background: #1d4ed8;
      color: white;
      font-size: .82rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .18em;
    }
    .eyebrow {
      font-size: .75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .2em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: .7rem;
    }
    .hero-card {
      border-radius: 1.4rem;
      border: 1px solid #1f2937;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(59,130,246,.25), #020617);
      padding: 1.5rem 1.4rem;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(15,23,42,.9);
      font-size: .9rem;
    }
    .hero-card h2 {
      font-family: "DM Serif Display", serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: .6rem;
    }
    .hero-card p {
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .hero-pill-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: .5rem;
    }
    .pill {
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: .18rem .7rem;
      border: 1px solid #4b5563;
      font-size: .7rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .13em;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }
    .pill.gold {
      border-color: #fbbf24;
      color: #fef3c7;
    }
    section {
      margin-top: 3.2rem;
    }
    h3 {
      font-family: "DM Serif Display", serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .two-col {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.8rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      .two-col {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
      }
    }
    .list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .list li {
      display: flex;
      gap: .6rem;
      margin-bottom: .9rem;
      font-size: .9rem;
    }
    .dot {
      width: 7px;
      height: 7px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #fbbf24, #b45309);
      margin-top: .4rem;
    }
    .gallery {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
      font-size: .85rem;
    }
    .gallery-card {
      border-radius: 1.1rem;
      border: 1px solid #1f2937;
      padding: 1rem .95rem;
      background: #020617;
    }
    .gallery-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: .35rem;
    }
    .tag {
      font-size: .7rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .15em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: .2rem;
    }
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid #111827;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding-top: 1.2rem;
      font-size: .75rem;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <header>
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="assets/logo-lovecrafted-digital.png"
             alt="Love Crafted Digital logo"
             class="logo-img">
      </div>
      <nav>
        <a href="#overview">Overview</a>
        <a href="#sections">Sections</a>
        <a href="#gallery">Gallery Layout</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero" id="overview">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Western x modern hybrid</div>
          <h1>Structured site with a bold blue, rope-heart brand feel.</h1>
          <p class="lede">
            This standard layout is built for service providers, photographers, and local brands that need more than a simple one-pager—without going full custom.
          </p>
          <a href="index.html" class="btn">Back to main site</a>
        </div>

        <aside class="hero-card">
          <h2>Layout highlights</h2>
          <p>
            Clear sections for services, story, social proof, and FAQs. Western details show up in typography and accents, but the overall feel stays clean and modern.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-pill-row">
            <span class="pill gold">Multi-page</span>
            <span class="pill">Service focused</span>
            <span class="pill">Photo-friendly</span>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <section id="sections">
        <h3>Core sections in this demo</h3>
        <div class="two-col">
          <ul class="list">
            <li>
              <span class="dot"></span>
              <span><strong>Hero & intro:</strong> clear tagline, quick description, and primary call-to-action.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="dot"></span>
              <span><strong>Services grid:</strong> 3–6 services, each with a short description and “starting at” prices.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="dot"></span>
              <span><strong>About section:</strong> your story, why you do what you do, and what makes you different.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="dot"></span>
              <span><strong>FAQ & details:</strong> answer common questions so clients feel confident before reaching out.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div style="font-size:.92rem; color:#9ca3af;">
            <p>
              On your real site, each section would be built from your actual copy, photos, and colors. This demo exists to show structure, spacing, and
              how the western-meets-modern style can look in practice.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top:1rem;">
              You can imagine this as a coffee shop, photographer, or pressure washing business—the bones stay the same, the visuals change to match your brand.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="gallery">
        <h3>Gallery & proof layout</h3>
        <div class="gallery">
          <article class="gallery-card">
            <div class="tag">Gallery row</div>
            <div class="gallery-title">Three-image strip</div>
            <p>
              Wide images in a row to show your work: before / after, favorite projects, or product highlights.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="gallery-card">
            <div class="tag">Testimonials</div>
            <div class="gallery-title">Quote cards</div>
            <p>
              Short client quotes with names and locations for social proof. Can be stacked or placed beside the gallery row.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="gallery-card">
            <div class="tag">Call to action</div>
            <div class="gallery-title">“Book now” strip</div>
            <p>
              A thin strip with a bold button to nudge visitors into reaching out once they’ve seen your work.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      © <span id="year"></span> Love Crafted Digital — Standard Demo
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.getElementById("year").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>

